24
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,520
We'll help clear your suspicion.

25
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,400
How to clear it?

26
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,159
According to him,

27
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,000
although Eye Plan

