52
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,520
Yes.

53
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,439
Use all your skills.

54
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,520
No problem.

55
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,280
