No.

137
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,560
Dream on.

138
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:12,920
How about it?

139
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,439
Right.

140
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,040
You know what?

141
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,519
That makes so much sense.

142
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:35,319
So,

143
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:36,360
Zhixing,

144
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,600
I knew from the start

145
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,879
