00:12:57,519 --> 00:12:58,840
is the only chance.

295
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,279
The radiation data
of the chemical plant.

296
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,159
It seems we can't go to Taipei.

297
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,759
Go contact Zheng Taixiang.

298
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:18,840
Tell him you've finally found evidence

299
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,759
that I'm a spy in contact
with Chinese mainland.

300
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,759
Bobo, what's wrong?

301
00:13:31,279 --> 00:13:33,080
I have already obtained the evidence

302
00:13:33,279 --> 00:13:34,159
that Anle is a spy.

303
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,240
What evidence?

304
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,720
But he is starting to suspect me.

305
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,440
To be on the safe side,

306
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,440
wait for my call.

307
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,679
I'll bring you the evidence tomorrow.

308
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,440
Okay.

309
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,799
When you meet up,

310
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,879
I'll go to his place to get something.

311
00:13:54,639 --> 00:13:55,480
Anle.

312
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,200
If you do this,

313
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,679
there's no turning back.

314
00:14:01,759 --> 00:14:02,559
I know.

315
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,799
Let's play a game.

316
00:14:06,799 --> 00:14:08,519
Let's see who finishes this first.

317
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,039
Shuang.

318
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:12,159
I'm not a kid anymore.

319
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:14,360
You want to trick me into drinking milk?

320
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,960
It's not that easy.

321
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,960
Are you scared?

322
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:19,120
Yes.

323
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,960
I am scared.

324
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,960
You're the best.

325
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:24,000
Keep going and finish it.

326
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,440
Good night, bye-bye.

327
00:14:33,639 --> 00:14:36,039
Why are kids now so difficult
to deal with?

328
00:14:36,759 --> 00:14:38,840
I remember that I was easy to trick
when I was a kid.

329
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:41,039
So why did you become bad
as you grew up?

330
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,799
Nice guys don't get the girl, right?

331
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,360
But I like obedient guys.

332
00:14:47,679 --> 00:14:48,799
I can be obedient, too.

333
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,360
I'm pure at heart.

334
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,600
I find your skin really thick

335
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,879
enough to tile the floor.

336
00:14:55,639 --> 00:14:56,960
Are you willing to

337
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,159
step on me hard?

338
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:00,759
You masochist. Stay away.

339
00:15:03,279 --> 00:15:03,840
My...

340
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,840
My wound hasn't healed.

341
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,440
This...

342
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,279
This part hurts.

343
00:15:07,279 --> 00:15:08,039
It hurts?

344
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,440
It really hurts.

345
00:15:10,399 --> 00:15:11,960
Then you should rest well.

346
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,000
Tonight, I'll

347
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:14,480
sleep with someone else.

348
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,000
I've suddenly gotten better.

349
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,519
The human body is amazing.

350
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,159
Come on.

351
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:30,159
There is still someone single
in this house, alright?

352
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,200
Sorry, Mr. Luo.

353
00:15:32,519 --> 00:15:33,559
Sorry?

354
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,279
You believe him?

355
00:15:35,279 --> 00:15:37,639
He's flirting with several ladies
at the same time

356
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:38,919
and won't take responsibility.

357
00:15:39,639 --> 00:15:41,360
I went there for you guys.

358
00:15:41,639 --> 00:15:42,759
What do you do for us?

359
00:15:42,759 --> 00:15:44,320
Drinking, fishing, and playing games?

360
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:45,960
Socializing.

361
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,320
(Long's Beef Noodles)
For you.

362
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:49,919
Mr. Luo.

363
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:52,639
Are you hungry?

364
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:01,679
Hello?

365
00:16:01,879 --> 00:16:03,120
Come see me tomorrow morning.

366
00:16:12,134 --> 00:16:15,951
♪When the name is buried in dust♪

367
00:16:15,951 --> 00:16:19,423
♪There's still a heartbeat
piercing through dawn and dusk♪

368
00:16:19,526 --> 00:16:23,347
♪If there's no applause for the ending♪

369
00:16:23,686 --> 00:16:29,682
♪At least the shadow
still makes a person♪
